Task 3: Live Chat/Contact Widget (Optional)

Add floating contact button:
- Fixed bottom-right corner
- Opens chat/contact popup
- Quick contact form
- Click-to-call phone number
- WhatsApp link
- Animated entrance

Task 4: Newsletter Signup

Add to footer:
- Email capture form
- "Get project inspiration" messaging
- Server action to save to database
- Success animation
